cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as entity and relation extraction. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses a transformer pre-training model and attention mechanisms. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses neural networks for its model architecture and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it deals with extracting information from text.
